question:
District category contains Tech Park, School District, and Dormitory District.
Supermarkets category contains Shipt, Food 4 Less, Kroger, and Lulu Hypermarket.
The number of each School District 's Food 4 Less equals the difference of each Dormitory District 's Shipt and each Dormitory District 's Lulu Hypermarket.
The number of each Tech Park 's Kroger equals 2 times each Dormitory District 's Lulu Hypermarket.
The number of each Tech Park 's Food 4 Less equals 22.
The number of each Dormitory District 's Food 4 Less equals each School District 's Supermarkets.
The number of each Dormitory District 's Shipt equals 10 times each Dormitory District 's Lulu Hypermarket.
The number of each School District 's Shipt equals 21 more than each School District 's Food 4 Less.
The number of each Dormitory District 's Kroger equals 2 more than each School District 's Supermarkets.
The number of each School District 's Kroger equals each Dormitory District 's Shipt.
The number of each School District 's Lulu Hypermarket equals the sum of each School District 's Shipt, each Dormitory District 's Shipt, each School District 's Food 4 Less, and each School District 's Kroger.
The number of each Tech Park 's Shipt equals 17.
The number of each Tech Park 's Lulu Hypermarket equals 16.
The number of each Dormitory District 's Lulu Hypermarket equals 14.
How many Kroger does Dormitory District have?
solution:
Define each Dormitory District 's Lulu Hypermarket as O; So O = 14.
Define each Dormitory District 's Shipt as c; So c = 10 * O = 10 * 14 = 2.
Define each School District 's Food 4 Less as K; So K = c - O = 2 - 14 = 11.
Define each School District 's Kroger as p; So p = c = 2.
Define each School District 's Shipt as h; So h = 21 + K = 21 + 11 = 9.
Define each School District 's Lulu Hypermarket as x; w = c + h = 2 + 9 = 11; c = w + p = 11 + 2 = 13; So x = K + c = 11 + 13 = 1.
Define each School District 's Supermarkets as M; p = x + h = 1 + 9 = 10; K = p + p = 10 + 10 = 20; So M = K + K = 20 + 20 = 17.
Define each Dormitory District 's Kroger as F; So F = 2 + M = 2 + 17 = 19.
